{"tid":1311581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點講得掂兩位黃絲老父母","createTime":"2019-07-13T09:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:42:09.000Z","uid":279513,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9e6e1519b262bc0d8374248c402cad85d2726a","tid":1311581,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"利申本人係和理非廢中, 但支持港獨革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩老六十幾, 都有讀過書會講道理嘅<br />\n民鼠黨fans, 每年64去坐三個鐘每年71行幾個鐘就覺得自己爭取到民主嗰隻<br />\n我成日都同佢講&ldquo;和平遊行係冇用架&quot;, 多謝今年71有巴絲幫我喺立法局寫左出黎<br />\n<br />\n自從71後我兩老都開始覺得齋行係冇L用<br />\n但係我有樣嘢成日拗唔掂我老豆, 佢成日話<br />\n&ldquo;港獨邊個去當兵? 係咪你去?&quot;<br />\n每次佢講呢樣就答唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫幫拖?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0fbcc0bb50b43107c3e8e79943187bf98cbf2d","tid":1311581,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"有錢請僱傭兵"},{"pid":"4893c5958c133aa70de28d5c94f501b2f1828115","tid":1311581,"uid":38991,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"交保護費比美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12758fa2f1edeb1fed00c3e31856e1ee2c447ed5","tid":1311581,"uid":133903,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:21:52.000Z","msg":"直接答佢，係"},{"pid":"e1b95c9ee80761976ce398f5011ea455ed4dfa96","tid":1311581,"uid":251775,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"如果國際間承認香港獨立 以香港金融上嘅地位 基本上國防同埋資源供給嘅問題大把人會同你諗計拆"},{"pid":"43b969c6d37f4e1576bbf1c685aaae4de09e190c","tid":1311581,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"學韓國 台灣 坡狗 成年男人當1~2年有咩問題"},{"pid":"48cbe29bd608854dd12bc5c148ce144218a333b5","tid":1311581,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12758fa2f1edeb1fed00c3e31856e1ee2c447ed5","tid":1311581,"uid":133903,"lik